sd=Prospect Campaign Management	Assess the coverage and impact of external/prospect campaigns and redirect campaign development and execution activity accordingly	Prospect Campaign Management identifies competitor activity that is targeting an untapped market segment. Campaign design is initiated to develop a competitive acquisition campaign to address the threat	Oversee the use and assess the coverage and impact of external/prospect campaigns. Direct prospect campaign execution resources to maximize business impact and in response to any identified market opportunities and threats. Oversee campaign design and development activity.
